🚀 Suggested Next Enhancements for Canvoras
	1.	Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
	•	Admin, Manager, Accountant, Salesperson, etc.
	•	Granular permissions (who can view/edit/export what).
	2.	Multi-Business Support
	•	Single user can manage multiple businesses under one account.
	•	Easy switching between businesses with isolated data.
	3.	Subscription & Payments
	•	Built-in Stripe / Razorpay integration for SaaS monetization.
	•	Tiered plans: Free → Pro → Enterprise.
	4.	Banking & Payments Integration
	•	Auto-import transactions from bank feeds (Open Banking APIs or Indian equivalents like ICICI, HDFC integrations).
	•	Payment reconciliation against invoices.
	5.	Smart AI Features (Differentiator)
	•	Predict low-stock reordering.
	•	GST filing assistant (auto-generate GSTR-1, GSTR-3B drafts).
	•	AI-powered insights: “Your sales dipped 15% this month compared to last.”
	6.	Offline-First Mode (Critical in India)
	•	PWA capability for Canvoras web → works offline.
	•	Syncs when internet is restored.
	7.	Data Backup & Migration Tools
	•	One-click backup/export for safety.
	•	Migration assistant from Tally/Marg CSVs.
	8.	Audit Logs & Compliance
	•	Every update tracked (who did what).
	•	Downloadable audit trails for CA/government compliance.
	9.	Mobile App (Future)
	•	Flutter app for business owners → create invoices, check stock, get analytics on the go.
	10.	Marketplace Ecosystem

	•	Allow plugins (e.g., payroll, HR, CRM add-ons).
	•	This can make Canvoras future-proof like Zoho.₹



